 head-to-head points; 3rd head-to-head goal difference; 4th head-to-head goals scored; 5th head-to-head away goals scored; 6th goal difference; 7th number of goals scored\n|update=complete\n|source=[http://www.frfotbal.ro/index.php?competition_id=14&season=0&serie_id=1284 FRF] {{in lang|ro}}\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Liga III seasons}}\n{{2016\u201317 in Romanian football}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Liga III 2016-17}}\n[[Category:Liga III seasons|2016]]\n[[Category:2016\u201317 in Romanian football|3]]\n[[Category:2016\u201317 in European third tier association football leagues|Romania]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football league season\n | country            = {{ROU}}\n | competition        = [[Liga III]]\n | season             = 2016\u201317\n | teams              = 73\n | promoted           = [[CS \u0218tiin\u021ba Miroslava|\u0218tiin\u021ba Miroslava]]<br/>[[FC Metaloglobus Bucure\u0219ti|Metaloglobus Bucure\u0219ti]]<br/>[[SCM Pite\u0219ti (football)|SCM Pite\u0219ti]]<br/>[[FC Ripensia Timi\u0219oara|Ripensia Timi\u0219oara]]<br/>[[FC Hermannstadt|Hermannstadt]]\n | relegated          = [[AFC Atletico Vaslui|Atletico Vaslui]]<br/>[[Sportul Chiscani]]<br/>[[SC Bac\u0103u (2010)|SC Bac\u0103u]]<br/>[[Petrolistul Bolde\u0219ti]]<br/>[[Arsenal Malu]]<br/>[[CS \u0218irineasa]]<br/>[[Urban Titu]]<br/>[[CS Podari]]<br/>[[FC UTA Arad|UTA II Arad]]<br/>[[CS Nuova Mama Mia Becicherecu Mic|NMM Becicherecu Mic]]<br/>[[ASA 2013 T\u00e2rgu Mure\u0219|ASA II T\u00e2rgu Mure\u0219]]<br/>[[CS O\u015forhei]]<br/>[[Recolta Dorol\u021b]]<br/>[[FC Bistri\u021ba]]\n | league topscorer   = [[Mediop Ndiaye]] (21) <br> ([[FC Ripensia Timi\u0219oara|Ripensia Timi\u0219oara]])\n | biggest home win   = [[\u00cenainte]]  14-1  [[Arsenal M.]]\n | biggest away win   = [[CSM Pa\u0219cani|Pa\u0219cani]]  1-7  [[AFC Atletico Vaslui|Atletico V.]]<br/>[[ACS Arsenal Malu|Arsenal M.]]  0-6  [[SC Pope\u0219ti-Leordeni|SC Pope\u0219ti]]<br/>[[ACS Arsenal Malu|Arsenal M.]]  0-6  [[CS Viitorul Domne\u0219ti|Domne\u0219ti]]\n | highest scoring    = [[\u00cenainte]]  14-1  [[Arsenal M.]]\n | matches            = 951\n | total goals        = 3027\n | longest wins       = 9 matches:<br />[[SCM Pite\u0219ti (football)|SCM Pite\u0219ti]]\n | longest unbeaten   = 28 matches:<br />[[SCM Pite\u0219ti (football)|SCM Pite\u0219ti]]\n | longest winless    = 26 matches:<br />[[ACS Arsenal Malu|Arsenal Malu]]\n | longest losses     = 26 matches:<br />[[ACS Arsenal Malu|Arsenal Malu]]\n | highest attendance = \n | lowest attendance  = \n | average attendance = \n | prevseason         = [[2015\u201316 Liga III|2015\u201316]]\n | nextseason         = [[2017\u201318 Liga III|2017\u201318]]\n | updated            = 26 May 2017\n}}\n\nThe '''2016\u201317 Liga III''' is the 61st season of the [[Liga III]], the third tier of the [[Romanian football league system]].  The season began on 2 September.<ref>{{cite news|title=Componen\u0163a celor cinci serii ale Ligii 3. 74 de echipe, posibil 75, vor participa \u00een noul sezon care \u00eencepe pe 2 \u015fi 3 septembrie|url=http://liga2.prosport.ro/liga-3/exclusiv-componenta-celor-cinci-serii-ale-ligii-3-74-de-echipe-posibil-75-vor-participa-in-noul-sezon-care-incepe-pe-2-si-3-septembrie-15611752|accessdate=25 August 2016|newspaper=ProSport}}</ref>\n\n== Team changes ==\n===To Liga III===\n'''Promoted from [[2015\u201316 Liga IV|Liga IV]]'''\n{{colbegin|colwidth=18em}}\n* [[Arsenal Malu]]\n* [[Av\u00e2ntul Valea M\u0103rului]]\n* [[Axiopolis Cernavod\u0103]]\n* [[Cetate R\u00e2\u0219nov]]\n* [[CS \u015eirineasa]]\n* [[CSM \u0218colar Re\u0219i\u021ba|CSM\u0218 Re\u0219i\u0163a]]\n* [[FC Bistri\u021ba]]\n* [[FC Hermannstadt]]\n* [[FCM Alexandria]]\n* [[CSM Flac\u0103ra Moreni|Flac\u0103ra Moreni]]\n* [[Gloria Lunca-Teuz Cermei]]\n* [[Mure\u0219ul Vin\u021bu de Jos]]\n* [[Petrolul Berca]] \n* [[Recolta Dorol\u021b]]\n* [[FC Ripensia Timi\u0219oara|Ripensia Timi\u0219oara]]\n* [[Sportul Chiscani]]\n* [[Viitorul Ulmeni]]\n{{colend}}\n'''Relegated from [[2015\u201316 Liga II|Liga II]]'''\n\u2014\n\n===From Liga III===\n'''Relegated to [[2016\u201317 Liga IV|Liga IV]]'''\n{{colbegin|colwidth=18em}}\n* [[CSM Bucovina R\u0103d\u0103u\u021bi|Bucovina R\u0103d\u0103u\u021bi]]\n* [[FC Zagon]]\n* [[FC Ozana T\u00e2rgu Neam\u021b|Cetatea T\u00e2rgu Neam\u021b]]\n* [[FC Callatis Mangalia|Callatis Mangalia]]\n* [[ACS Inter Olt Slatina|Inter Olt Slatina]]\n* [[CSM Sighetu Marma\u0163iei]]\n* [[Luceaf\u0103rul B\u0103lan]]\n{{colend}}\n'''Promoted to [[2016\u201317 Liga II|Liga II]]'''\n{{colbegin|colwidth=18em}}\n* [[Sepsi OSK Sf\u00e2ntu Gheorghe|Sepsi Sf\u00e2ntu Gheorghe]]\n* [[CS Juventus Bucure\u0219ti|Juventus Bucure\u0219ti]]\n* [[CS Afuma\u021bi|Afuma\u021bi]]\n* [[ASU Politehnica Timi\u0219oara]]\n* [[CS Luceaf\u0103rul Oradea|Luceaf\u0103rul Oradea]]\n{{colend}}\n\n===Teams spared from relegation===\n[[ACS Foresta Suceava|Foresta Suceava]], [[CS Unirea T\u0103rlungeni|Unirea T\u0103rlungeni]] and [[CSM Metalul Re\u0219i\u021ba|Metalul Re\u0219i\u021ba]] were spared from relegation to [[Liga III]] due to lack of teams in [[Liga II]].<ref>http://www.gsp.ro/fotbal/liga-b/burleanu-a-chemat-comitetul-de-urgenta-pentru-o-sedinta-fulger-frf-a-decis-echipele-care-vor-juca-sezonul-viitor-in-liga-a-2-a-484905.html</ref>\n\n===Excluded teams===\nAfter the end of the last season, [[ACS Bucovina Pojor\u00e2ta|Bucovina Pojor\u00e2ta]], [[FCM Dorohoi|Dorohoi]], [[FC Caransebe\u0219|Caransebe\u0219]] and [[Muscelul C\u00e2mpulung]] were dissolved. [[FC O\u021belul Gala\u021bi|O\u021belul Gala\u021bi]], [[FC Universitatea Cluj|Universitatea Cluj]] and [[FC Bihor Oradea|Bihor Oradea]] were also dissolved, but refounded in the middle of 2016 and enrolled in [[Liga IV]] respectively [[Liga V]].\n\n[[FC Farul Constan\u021ba|Farul Constan\u021ba]] dropped out from the [[Liga II]] due to financial difficulties and enrolled in [[Liga III]], but then were excluded from [[Liga III]] also.<ref>http://liga2.prosport.ro/seria-1/fc-farul-nu-va-juca-in-liga-3-si-intra-in-faliment-seria-a-ii-a-ramane-cu-14-echipe-asa-cum-va-fi-mai-nou-si-cazul-seriei-a-iv-a-15636751</ref>\n\n[[FC Ceahl\u0103ul Piatra Neam\u021b|Ceahl\u0103ul Piatra Neam\u021b]] and [[FC Gloria Buz\u0103u|Gloria Buz\u0103u]] were relegated to [[Liga V]], because the teams were excluded during the [[2015\u201316 Liga II]] season.\n\n[[CS Panciu]] and [[FC Hunedoara]] were excluded from [[Liga III]].\n\n[[M\u0103gura Cisn\u0103die]] and [[Inter Dorohoi]] withdrew from [[Liga III]].\n\n[[Sporting Turnu M\u0103gurele]] and [[CS Minerul Motru|Minerul Motru]] withdrew from [[Liga III]] and dissolved their senior teams, but remain with their youth centers.\n\n[[CS Ineu]] withdrew from [[Liga III]] and enrolled in [[Liga IV]] due to financial difficulties.\n\n[[CS Unirea T\u0103rlungeni|Unirea T\u0103rlungeni]] was moved from [[T\u0103rlungeni]] to [[\u0218tef\u0103ne\u0219tii de Jos]] and took all the players and the staff from [[CS \u0218tef\u0103ne\u0219ti]]. [[CS \u0218tef\u0103ne\u0219ti]] was dissolved.\n\n[[CSM Metalul Re\u0219i\u021ba|Metalul Re\u0219i\u021ba]] was moved from [[Re\u0219i\u0163a]] to [[Snagov]] and took all the players and the staff of [[AS Voin\u021ba Snagov|Voin\u021ba Snagov]] which was dissolved.\n\n[[FC Arge\u0219 1953 Pite\u015fti|Arge\u0219 1953 Pite\u0219ti]], [[CS P\u0103ule\u0219ti]], [[Mure\u0219ul Vin\u021bu de Jos]], [[Petrolul Berca]], [[Siretul Lespezi]] and [[Voin\u021ba Ion Creang\u0103]] declined participation in [[Liga III]] due to lack of funds.\n\n===Other teams===\n[[SC Bac\u0103u (2010)|SC Bac\u0103u]] withdrew from [[Liga II]] due to financial difficulties and enrolled in [[Liga III]].<ref>http://liga2.prosport.ro/seria-1/luni-aflam-componenta-noului-sezon-al-ligii-2-situatia-echipelor-in-acest-moment-farul-a-renuntat-sc-bacau-o-poate-urma-iar-baia-mare-si-a-anulat-decizia-de-excludere-15544920</ref>\n\n[[ACS Poli Timi\u0219oara]], [[ASA 2013 T\u00e2rgu Mure\u0219|ASA T\u00e2rgu Mure\u0219]], [[FC Astra Giurgiu|Astra Giurgiu]], [[CS Mioveni]], [[CS Gaz Metan Media\u0219|Gaz Metan Media\u0219]], [[FC Steaua Bucure\u0219ti|Steaua Bucure\u0219ti]] and [[FC UTA Arad|UTA Arad]] enrolled in [[Liga III]] their second teams.\n\n[[FC Unirea Alba Iulia|Unirea Alba Iulia]] received the permission to enroll in [[Liga III]], due to the excellent results recorded in the youth championships.\n\n===Renamed teams===\nPetrotub Roman was renamed as [[CSM Roman]].\n\nGloria Pope\u0219ti-Leordeni was renamed as [[SC Pope\u0219ti-Leordeni]].\n\n==League tables==\n\n===Seria I===\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=PR\n\n|team1=MIR|name_MIR=[[CS \u0218tiin\u021ba Miroslava|\u0218tiin\u021ba Miroslava]]\n|team2=H\u0102R|name_H\u0102R=[[AFC H\u0103rman|H\u0103rman]]\n|team3=MIE|name_MIE=[[FK Miercurea Ciuc|Miercurea Ciuc]]\n|team4=AER|name_AER=[[CS Aerostar Bac\u0103u|Aerostar Bac\u0103u]]\n|team5=AVM|name_AVM=[[CS Av\u00e2ntul Valea M\u0103rului|Av\u00e2ntul Valea M\u0103rului]]\n|team6=ROM|name_ROM=[[CSM Roman (football)|Roman]]\n|team7=OCT|name_OCT=[[ACS Olimpic Cetate R\u00e2\u0219nov|Olimpic Cetate R\u00e2\u0219nov]]\n|team8=SPO|name_SPO=[[Sporting Lie\u0219ti]]\n|team9=ORM|name_ORM=[[Olimpia R\u00e2mnicu S\u0103rat]]\n|team10=MTS|name_MTS=[[Metalosport Gala\u021bi]]\n|team11=VAS|name_VAS=[[AFC Atletico Vaslui|Atletico Vaslui]]\n|team12=ODO|name_ODO=[[AFC Odorheiu Secuiesc|Odorheiu Secuiesc]]\n|team13=PA\u0218|name_PA\u0218=[[CSM Pa\u0219cani|Pa\u0219cani]]\n|team14=SCH|name_SCH=[[Sportul Chiscani]]\n|team15=BAC|name_BAC=[[SC Bac\u0103u (2010)|SC Bac\u0103u]]\n|win_MIR=20|draw_MIR=4|loss_MIR=4|gf_MIR=65|ga_MIR=31|status_MIR=C,P\n|win_H\u0102R=19|draw_H\u0102R=6|loss_H\u0102R=3|gf_H\u0102R=63|ga_H\u0102R=19\n|win_MIE=19|draw_MIE=6|loss_MIE=3|gf_MIE=61|ga_MIE=18\n|win_AER=14|draw_AER=6|loss_AER=8|gf_AER=47|ga_AER=29\n|win_AVM=13|draw_AVM=4|loss_AVM=11|gf_AVM=49|ga_AVM=53\n|win_ROM=12|draw_ROM=4|loss_ROM=12|gf_ROM=48|ga_ROM=50\n|win_OCT=11|draw_OCT=